description: The SPDR S&P Emerging Asia Pacific ETF seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the total return performance of the S&P Emerging Asia Pacific BMI Index (the “Index”)Seeks to provide broad exposure to Asia Pacific emerging market countries, which offers the potential for investors to take strategic or tactical positions in the regionCould potentially mitigate country-specific risk
name: SPDR S&P Emerging Asia Pacific ETF
